</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div><img style="max-width: 100%; float: right;" src="/media/13051390/chef.jpg" alt="Chef" rel="245,102" /></div>
<h3>“We thoroughly enjoyed every aspect of our holiday. I would highly recommend Inghams for the high quality in terms of hospitality and staff training. Nothing is left to chance; we were highly impressed with every detail.”</h3>
<p> </p>
<p><em>Mrs B. Press, Chalet Hotel Montfort, Lech, September 2016</em></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>What’s included</h2>
<ul>
<li>Friendly service from your Inghams Chalet Hotel team or chalet hosts</li>
<li>Your choice of room (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Comfortable accommodation - mostly with rooms with private en suite facilities</li>
<li>Knowledge staff to help you get the most out of your holiday</li>
<li>All properties are non-smoking</li>
<li>Free wi-fi in public areas</li>
</ul>
<br /><strong> Half-Board PLUS </strong>includes the following<strong>:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Daily buffet breakfast (with hot option in Chalet Hotels)</li>
<li>Packed lunches</li>
<li>Afternoon tea, coffee &amp; cake</li>
<li>Excellent 4 or 5 course evening meals with an apéritif</li>
<li>Choice of complimentary quality wines, tea, coffee &amp; chocolates</li>
<li>Weekly barbecue or al fresco evening</li>
</ul>
<br />
<p>Vegetarian options are always available on our menus at no extra cost, and other special diets can be catered for at a cost of £35 per person per week, if booked in advance. All Chalet Hotels are entirely non-smoking. Property ratings displayed on the accommodation page(s) are our own, and are not to be confused with any 'official' star ratings systems. Further information can be found in our <a href="/{localLink:66d6dfd2-b127-48e8-b6d8-228d6e59ea65}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">Terms and Conditions</a>.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Complimentary Chalet Wines</h2>
<p>Our choice of wines is selected in conjunction with our good friends, Nicolas and Véronique Perret, and their long established Savoie wine business. Nicolas is a qualified ‘Master of Wine’, and has helped us select two contrasting whites, two choice reds and a rosé for you to enjoy, unlimited, throughout dinner each evening.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Our Chalet Hotel Staff</h2>
<p>Our Chalet Hotel Hosts are chosen for their friendly and helpful attitude, whilst our Head Chefs and their teams are professionally trained to provide consistently enjoyable restaurant-standard cuisine. At all times your Resort Representative is also on hand to help out with their local knowledge, and to arrange local restaurant bookings on the Chalet Hotel team’s one day off per week.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
</div>
