<h3>Inghams Chalet Hotels <br />Sample Culinary Choice Menu</h3>
<p><strong><br />CANAPÉS </strong><br />Creamed Goat's Cheese &amp; Basil en Croûte<br />or Spicy Ragu on Sweet Potato Crisps<br /><br /><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★<br /></span><br /><strong>CHOICE OF STARTER</strong><br />Minestrone Soup with Herb Croutons &amp; Crispy Leeks<br />or Fresh Tomato and Mozzarella Tart served with a Basil Dressing</p>
<p><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★</span> <br /><br /><strong>MAIN COURSE</strong><br />Slow Roast Lamb with Sundried Tomato Sauce,<br />or Lemon and Thyme Chicken Supreme<br /><br /><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★</span></p>
<p><strong>VEGETARIAN OPTION</strong><br />Spring Onion, Feta Cheese and Frittata with Dill Cream<br /><br /><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★</span></p>
<p><span>All main courses served with </span><span>Summer Vegetables<br /></span><br /><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★</span></p>
<p><strong>CHOICE OF DESSERT</strong><br />Baked Apple Strudel with Crème Anglaise<br />or Dark Chocolate &amp; Orange Liqueur Tiramisu<br /><br /><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★</span></p>
<p><strong>COFFEE OR TEA WITH PETIT FOURS</strong></p>
<p><span style="color: #fcaf17; font-size: 10px;">★★★★<br /></span><br />Our Complimentary Selection of Red,<br />White and Rosé Wines each evening</p>
